            <title>[SOLR-15384] Zookeeper admin handlers not queryable from SolrJ</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-15384</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Trying to do a raw SolrJ request to &lt;tt&gt;/solr/admin/zookeeper/status&lt;/tt&gt; but it fails with exception and message &quot;No collection param specified on request and no default collection has been set&quot;, since the path is not in the&#160;&lt;tt&gt;ADMIN_PATHS&lt;/tt&gt; set of CommonParams, thus SolrJ believes it is querying a handler inside a core, not an admin-level path.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
